metadata.name: Comugi
metadata.description:
Assumed his current position after working as an editor of business books, as the Editor-in-Chief of Crypto Web Media in Japan, and as a producer of Japan's largest blockchain conference.
He provided infographics and supervision to the “Web3” special feature in Volume 44 of the Japan version of WIRED magazine. He also attends conferences such as Web3 Conference Tokyo and actively posts about the latest Web3 developments under the name “Comugi” and using the “@ro_mi” handle on Twitter.
